  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You collect wind release chakra and infuse it into your Medical Release technique. One willing creature within range breathes in this Medically infused wind.</p><p>For the duration a creature who has breathed this wind does not need to breathe, Ignores the effects of 1 rank of Exhaustion and when they would regain hit points as the result of a Ninjutsu with the Medical Keyword, they regain an additional 1d4 Hit points.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, Ignores the effects of up to 1 additional rank of Exhaustion.</p>",
